    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Eutrombicula helleri (Oudemans, 1911)—specimen ZIN 8852, Peru. A—general view, B—dorsal aspect of idiosoma, C—scutum, D—ventral aspect of idiosoma. Scale bars: 100 µm (A), 50 µm (B–D)." ;
