<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6598092>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Eutrombicula goeldii (Oudemans, 1910). A—scutum and eyes (specimen ZIN 8829), B—dorsal idiosomal seta (specimen ZIN 8829), C—ventral idiosomal seta (specimen ZIN 8829), D—ventral aspect of idiosoma (specimen ZIN 8830), E—dorsal aspect of idiosoma (specimen ZIN 8830), F—ventral aspect of gnathosoma (specimen ZIN 8829), G—dorsal aspect of gnathosoma (specimen ZIN 8829). Abbreviations as in Fig. 2. Scale bars: 50 µm (A), 20 µm (B, C, F, G), 100 µm (D, E)." ;
